============================================================
|ID|OPERATOR           |NAME         |EST.ROWS|EST.TIME(us)|
------------------------------------------------------------
|0 |SORT               |             |15      |50          |
|1 |└─HASH DISTINCT    |             |15      |48          |
|2 |  └─TABLE FULL SCAN|t2(idx_t2_c1)|15      |43          |
============================================================
